questions.statement:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Directions: &lt;/strong&gt;Study the following line graph and answer the question based on it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Number of Vehicles Manufactured by Two companies over the Years&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(Number in thousands)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/21/04/DI_15-04_2021_vaibhav_umesh_D%203.PNG&quot; style=&quot;width: 484px; height: 355px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
What is the difference between the total productions of the two companies from 1997 to 2000?&lt;/p&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 400px;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;tbody&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;1997&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;1998&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;1999&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;2000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;2001&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;2002&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;X&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;119&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;99&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;141&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;78&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;120&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;159&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;139&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;120&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;100&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;128&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;107&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;148&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
	&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Sum of vehicles manufactured in the give years by company X =&amp;nbsp;119 + 99 + 141 + 78 = 437&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Sum of vehicles manufactured in the given years by company Y = 139 + 120 + 100 + 128 = 487&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Difference = 487000 - 437000&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; 50000&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Therefore, difference between the total productions of the two companies from 1997 to 2000 is 50000&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
